Author: color_me_skinny
Text: It's hard because I know the right thing is to recover. But idk if I could live with myself at a higher weight. I already feel too big

Author: tigerchik
Text: I honestly believe if you don't want to recover, you shouldn't have to. If you can find a reason to recover, like doing it for your SO, that's great. And if you want to wait, eventually you'll either get miserable enough to want recovery, or you won't.
